<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1078826" n="1r"/>
<opener><salute>Viro Clarissimo ac Pereximio
             <lb/>Petro Antonio <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Michelotti</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
<lb/><abbr>Joh.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs></salute></opener>
<p>Ecce ad humanissimam Tuam invitationem Tibi mitto <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Filium</rs> meum<!-- Nicolaus II, sagt Fritz -->; tantum
             <lb/>fuit ejus desiderium tanta<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> cupido exteras Terras visendi, ut viris egregiis bene<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> meritis
             <lb/>quos inter Te primum numeravit, innotescendi, ut laudabilem ejus ardorem restinguere nec po<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tuerim nec voluerim. Spero illum ita se gesturum, ut Te nunquam p<choice><orig><g ref="#oe">œ</g></orig><reg>oe</reg></choice>niteat, eum simul in hos<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pitium et amicitiam Tuam venisse; forte secum adferet, quo satisfacere Tibi possit in iis qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>telligere voles de abstrusioribus mathematum mysteriis: rogo tantum ut indulgeas nonnihil ejus ju<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ventuti, sicubi proponas quandam difficultatem ad quam <choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> vestigio non respondeat, hoc enim
             <lb/>arduum est exercitatissimis magistris, s<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>p<choice><orig><g ref="#eacut">é</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice><choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> accidit ut opus habeant mor<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> non brevi, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> se extricent
             <lb/>ex labyrintho. C<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terum vero <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Filius</rs> meus Te pro virili su<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> juvabit, Te venerabitur ut Patrem suum
             <lb/>Tibi<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> ut Patri suo in omnibus licitis et honestis obedientiam promtissimam pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stabit: Eum ita<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>
             <lb/>cur<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Patern<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> enixissime commendo; sancte promittens me meum<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Filium</rs> per omnem
             <lb/>nostram vitam omnia qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te accipiet beneficia juxta benevolentiam, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> eum honorabis
             <lb/>ubi<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> et semper esse depr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dicaturos et mente gratissima memori<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> nostr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> impressuros.
             <lb/>Quod si vero contingeret ut pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ter spem illum non talem deprehenderes qualem optabas et
             <lb/>expectabas, aut ob quamcun<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> aliam causam illius pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>senti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> fieres pert<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sus, Tibi uti<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>
             <lb/>foret tunc<!-- "foret" und "tunc" im Original vertauscht, Reihenfolge mit Nummern angezeigt. --> integrum, illum iterum dimittere, id enim pro certo habeas Vir <choice><abbr>Clariss.</abbr><expan>Clarissime</expan></choice> quod ego quam
             <lb/>maxime dolerem, si vel per momentum <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Filius</rs> meus Tibi molestus ejusve pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentia grav<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>is esset: quare Te rogo, ut in tali casu illum dimittere nullum scrupulum facias
             <lb/>nec qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so verearis, me e<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> re offensum iri. Sin ex adverso satis, quod spero et voveo, felix fu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>turus est, ut Tibi placere possit, eam certe in Te habeo confidentiam, ut ausim porro spe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rare fore ut <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Filius</rs> meus Te adjuvante aliquando honestam stationem quandam apud vos
             <lb/>vel in vicini<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> vestra impetret, nisi forte omnino in <choice><sic>Archyliceo</sic><corr><rs type="organisation">Archilyceo</rs></corr></choice> Patavino operam suam
             <lb/>collocandi inveniat occasionem; huic ad votum meum consequendo fini multum, opinor, con<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tribuet, si Te introductore et commendatore <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Filius</rs> meus accessum favorabilem habere
             <lb/>possit apud Viros Nobiles at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> Proceres, qui <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> rerum summam gerunt, qui<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> ut
             <lb/>scio Tibi faventissimi sunt, ob felicissimam et expertissimam Tuam Praxin medicam,
             <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> quotidianam Tibi pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>bet eos visendi occasionem. Nihil pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terea addo; nisi ut dicam
             <lb/>me intellexisse <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <choice><abbr>Dno.</abbr><expan>Domino</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118571249" type="person">Leibnitio</rs>, quod <choice><abbr>Dn.</abbr><expan>Dominus</expan></choice> Comes <rs key="pers_DE-588-118642286" type="person">Schulenburgius</rs>, qui in negotio Patavin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> voca<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tionis se laboraturum promisit propediem iter faciet, nisi quod credo jam fecerit in <choice><orig>dal<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>matiam</orig><reg>Dalmatiam</reg></choice>, quid autem effecerit, aut quous<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> hoc negotium promoverit, sibi quidem non
             <lb/>constare addidit <rs key="pers_DE-588-118571249" type="person">Leibnitius</rs>: <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Filius</rs> meus hoc melius ex Te ipso intelliget: <choice><orig>Jnterim</orig><reg>Interim</reg></choice>
<lb/>mensis spatium (intra quod Te pro certo dicere posse an succedat vel non succedat ad
             <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnatum</rs> meum scripsisti) jamjam ut mihi vide<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice> est elapsum.</p> <closer><salute>Quod superest
                <lb/>Vir Clarissime ab <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person"><choice><sic>Agnoto</sic><corr>Agnato</corr></choice></rs> meo et a me quam officiosissime salutatus Vale et fave.</salute>
<lb/><dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice> <date when="1716-03-10">10<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> Mart. 1716.</date></dateline></closer>
